    "body": "GitHub source links use `git archive`, which does not support submodules. We have asked GitHub for the ability to remove these links, since they are confusing to people, and we have no control over them. You can get a 'full' source version of IPython, either [on PyPI](https://pypi.python.org/simple/ipython/) or [archive.ipython.org](http://archive.ipython.org/release).\n"
